this_title: The Tonight Show Starring Johnny Carson:The Best of Stand-Up
introduction: Relive some of the funniest moments ever from Johnny Carson's Tonight Show, in this hilarious 2-disc set of stand-up comedians,who made their debut at Johnny's side. Includes Jerry Seinfeld, Rodney Dangerfield, George Carlin, Brett Butler, Roseanne Barr, Drew Carey, Louie Anderson, Garry Shandling, and many more. If Carson was the King of late night, these were his favorite court jesters!
